high_descs: approach the counter to the left of the sink
pick up the knife from the counter
take the knife to the counter to your right where the loaf of bread is
cut the tomato to the left
walk the knife over to the dishwasher behind you
stand the knife up by it's tip on the counter above the dishwasher
walk back to the counter with the bread and sliced tomato
pick up the tomato slice
take the slice to the fridge
put the slice in the fridge, wait, then remove
take the slice to the the microwave
cook the slice in the microwave
anns.task_desc: cut a slice of tomato, chill it, then cook it in the microwave

high_descs: Turn to the left, go forward, hang a right, go to the counter between the stove and sink.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that is on the counter.
Hang a right, go to the counter where the bread is.
Cut the tomato that is to the left of the bread on the counter into slices.
Turn to the left to the counter where the coffee maker is.
Put the knife down on the counter.
Turn to the counter on the right.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the counter.
Turn around, go across the room to the fridge that is on the right.
Put the tomato in the fridge and close the door, remove the tomato once it is cold.
Turn around, go forward, hang a left and go to the microwave.
Put the slice of tomato in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put cold slice of tomato in the microwave.

high_descs: Walk forwards towards the counter on the left of the sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Make a right to walk to the counter above the dishwasher.
Slice the tomato on the counter.
Turn to face the counter to the left of the coffee machine.
Set the knife down on the counter.
Turn to face the tomato on the counter.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the counter.
Make a left to walk to the fridge.
Chill the tomato in the fridge, talking it back out afterwards.
Make a left to walk to the microwave.
Put the tomato slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Slice a tomato to chill in the fridge and leave in the microwave.
